{
  "stem": "150.1",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But just because you were chained to a wall in Beirut for five years doesn't make you a hero because you would much rather be in Chicago.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You don't have a choice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I'm not a hero because I would have much rather grown up in New York or Malibu or Paris.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I didn't have that choice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I'm not a hero.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But there are heroes, and there was heroism.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There were-- there were Jewish policemen in the ghetto, Jewish young men who wore armbands that [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they kept order.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They organized the labor brigades and so on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The Germans knew that there were a lot of hiding places in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And as you saw in there were false ceilings and false walls.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And you could go through an oven into somewhere under the house.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They called them malinas.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Malinas were the hiding places.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And the Germans took the 300 ghetto police to the Ninth Fort.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they told them, they said, each one of you must betray a malina.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Surely you know where they are.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And those who tell us where they are will be allowed to go back in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Those who don't talk, sorry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "You're not going anywhere.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And they gave them 72 hours.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And after 72 hours, out of the 300 12 came back. 288 died.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Nobody knows their names.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Nobody will ever know their names.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "That is heroism, you know, not just surviving or whatever.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, what happened then, our numbers kept getting smaller and smaller, and the Russians started fighting back real well.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as the front came nearer, they decided to evacuate those of us who were left, take us to slave labor to Germany.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
